{
  "stem": "22685.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Under Russian occupation, we were supposed to be shipped out of our town, because people-- let's say-- who have-- who-- so-called capitalists, but, of course, it was exaggeration.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were supposed to be shipped out of our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as my father had a background of a revolutionary, we wrote to Stalin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got an answer from Stalin that if they had the background-- so they left us, and they gave us back our house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he started to work for the city government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a supplier of wood and everything for the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to a college, they didn't-- which was a physics-mathematics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And until the war broke out, I was in this college.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Life became normal, and not normal, because they didn't change to a communist system overnight.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- it took-- they were-- they had all kinds of plans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, the war disrupted the plans, but a lot of Jews felt much better under the Soviet domination than under the Polish discrimination.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When war broke out, my father wasn't home, so I had to stay with the mother with the kids.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to go from our house to some relatives, cousins, because all the-- we lived close to the main street, and all the traffic of tanks was going 24 hours to the front.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we just-- my mother didn't have the nerves to support this, so we went to-- to a cousin's, that they lived on a side street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until my father came back-- when my father came back, on the third day of the war-- the war broke out the 22nd of June, 1941.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Anyhow, the 25th, I left home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was back.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
